sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as kueue-webhook-service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant Controller as kueue-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    participant Scheduler as Scheduler Engine
    participant Cache as In-Memory Cache
    participant Job as Batch Job
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Autoscaler as Cluster Autoscaler

    %% Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Job: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create job<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (User)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS (API Server client cert)
        Webhook->>Webhook: Inject queue annotation<br/>Set suspend=true
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Modified Job spec
        K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Job resources<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job created event
        Controller->>Controller: Create Workload CR<br/>for Job
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Workload<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)

        Controller->>Scheduler: Evaluate admission<br/>for Workload
        Scheduler->>Cache: Check ClusterQueue quota<br/>and priorities
        Cache-->>Scheduler: Quota available
        Scheduler-->>Controller: Admit workload

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch Job (suspend=false)<br/>Inject node selectors<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
        K8sAPI->>Job: Start pods
        Job-->>K8sAPI: Job running
    end

    %% Flow 2: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prom,Controller: Flow 2: Metrics Collection
        Prom->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)<br/>HTTPS/8443
        Controller-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(pending workloads, admissions)
    end

    %% Flow 3: Visibility API Query
    rect rgb(255, 250, 230)
        Note over User,Cache: Flow 3: Visibility API Query
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl get --raw /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/...<br/>Bearer Token (User)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Forward to visibility API<br/>K8s RBAC validation
        Controller->>Cache: Query pending workloads<br/>(in-process, no network)
        Cache-->>Controller: Workload list
        Controller-->>K8sAPI: JSON response
        K8sAPI-->>User: Pending workloads
    end

    %% Flow 4: Provisioning Request (Autoscaling)
    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Controller,Autoscaler: Flow 4: Provisioning Request (Autoscaling)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ProvisioningRequest<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: PR created
        Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: Watch ProvisioningRequests<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>Autoscaler: PR created event
        Autoscaler->>Autoscaler: Provision nodes<br/>via cloud provider API
        Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: Update PR status<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch PR status<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Nodes ready
        Controller->>Scheduler: Re-evaluate admission
    end
